# VigilAura - Personal Safety Application üö®

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)
![Flask](https://img.shields.io/badge/flask-2.0+-green.svg)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-orange.svg)

VigilAura is a Flask-based web application designed to enhance personal safety through emergency alerts, fake calls, and location sharing.

## Features ‚ú®

- **SOS Alert**: Instantly notify trusted contacts via email
- **Fake Call**: Simulate an incoming call to deter threats
- **Location Sharing**: Share your current location (future implementation)
- **Simple Web Interface**: Easy-to-use one-click controls

